        {
            "title": "油麗邨14歲少女暈倒 父親發現報惜送院不治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"油麗邨14歲少女暈倒，父親發現報惜送院不治。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/24e4dbf428a8a8ebf162525e55bd7ac8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040501112753790.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">油麗邨14歲少女暈倒，父親發現報惜送院不治。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周五（4日）晚上7時許，警方接獲一名男子報案，指發現其14歲女兒在油麗邨卓麗樓一單位內暈倒。救援人員接報到場，發現女事主倒臥在單位客廰，她清醒被送往聯合醫院治理，其後被證實死亡。死因有待驗屍後確定。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177716/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"女事主清醒被送往聯合醫院治理，其後被證實死亡。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c4879350bef5eafd24db7c2f6e44e460/2025-04/UC2.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女事主清醒被送往聯合醫院治理，其後被證實死亡。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062189/即時-港聞-油麗邨14歲少女暈倒-父親發現報惜送院不治",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-05 01:16:09",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "一鍋端｜中國舞協主席馮雙白書記羅斌 涉嫌嚴重違法被查",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"中國舞協主席馮雙白書記羅斌涉嫌嚴重違法被查。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d6dc01b55731c0288901946a7e456f5e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040423564335153.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">中國舞協主席馮雙白書記羅斌涉嫌嚴重違法被查。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>官方昨日公布，中國舞蹈家協會主席馮雙白，中國舞蹈家協會原分黨組書記、駐會副主席羅斌涉嫌嚴重違紀違法，目前正接受調查。\n\n</p>\n<p>71歲的馮雙白是內地知名舞蹈理論家、舞劇編劇，曾編劇《金陵十三釵》等大型演出，曾任全國政協委員。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177669/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"中國舞蹈家協會主席馮雙白。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d70a97fbb4e421f70b5d36d322a6f6c/2025-04/12345.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        中國舞蹈家協會主席馮雙白。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177670/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"中國舞蹈家協會原分黨組書記、駐會副主席羅斌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6bfc30aaf07561fb680655fc286eeb9/2025-04/54321.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        中國舞蹈家協會原分黨組書記、駐會副主席羅斌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>中國文聯舞蹈藝術中心藝術交流處副處長韋立（女），昨日同被通報涉嫌嚴重違紀違法被查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177671/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"中國文聯舞蹈藝術中心藝術交流處副處長韋立。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8a573cd1bbd68addd71d1c7a92633427/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-04_at_16_43_41_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        中國文聯舞蹈藝術中心藝術交流處副處長韋立。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>韋立為中國舞蹈家協會社會舞蹈教育委員會秘書長、協會《中國舞蹈考級》教材執行副主任。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062188/即時-中國-一鍋端-中國舞協主席馮雙白書記羅斌-涉嫌嚴重違法被查",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-05 00:41:36",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國關稅｜被徵46%關稅 特朗普：越南希望將其關稅降至零",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"特朗普與蘇林通話，稱對方希望將關稅降至零。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d6d04d2089c5c37b3eebd576a9dc48f6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040423490624536.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">特朗普與蘇林通話，稱對方希望將關稅降至零。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國總統特朗普日前推出「對等關稅」，涉及180多個國家和地區，其中東南亞國家越南被美國徵收百分之46的對等關稅，特朗普周五與越共總書記蘇林進行對話。\n\n</p>\n<p>特朗普周五（4月4日）在社交平台上表示，剛剛與越南共產黨中央總書記蘇林進行了一次非常有成效的通話，他告訴我，如果越南能夠與美國達成協議，他們希望將關稅降至零。我代表美國向他表示感謝，並表示我期待在不久的將來舉行會晤。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177654/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"特朗普在其社交平台發文，稱蘇林希望將關稅降至零。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b32dcfab85cd098ea96ce19a21c006a4/2025-04/2025-04-04_23_24_55.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普在其社交平台發文，稱蘇林希望將關稅降至零。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177655/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"美國總統特朗普日前推出「對等關稅」，涉及180多個國家和地區。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/31510ee23f33ea996a6a0598e9d7558a/2025-04/2025-04-04T031039Z_159449368_RC2JQDA4M9CQ_RTRMADP_3_USA-TRUMP.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美國總統特朗普日前推出「對等關稅」，涉及180多個國家和地區。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177656/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"特朗普：越南希望將其關稅降至零。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43b8dc66b407069b38cf88017fd9de40/2025-04/2025-04-04T105932Z_234904096_RC2XPDAC0YJR_RTRMADP_3_USA-TRUMP-TARIFFS-RATINGS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        特朗普：越南希望將其關稅降至零。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062187/即時-國際-美國關稅-被徵46-關稅-特朗普-越南希望將其關稅降至零",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-05 00:21:37",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
