        {
            "title": "控煙酒辦銅鑼灣放蛇控3人吸水煙 另揭樓上酒吧無酒牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/eaf95496b9c189ae6a16dfc10bda992e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250404/_2025040423362443074.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>衞生署控煙酒辦今晚（4日）到銅鑼灣打擊禁煙區非法吸食水煙的情況，行動中人員到渣甸街66號一間樓上酒吧「放蛇」及執法，向1名酒吧負責人、1名職員及1名顧客發出在室內吸煙的告票，並檢走兩支水煙。\n\n</p>\n<p>據了解，涉事酒吧經營約3年，負責人聲稱正在續牌，故暫時沒有酒牌，水煙售價為400元，加續一次為200元。控煙酒辦人員到場時發現負責人及職員正在店內吸食水煙，同時又招待顧客吸食水煙，3人當場被票控在室內吸煙。\n\n</p>\n<p>控煙酒辦稍後會向律政司索取指示，了解是否檢控該場地負責人及職員，涉嫌協助教唆他人在室內吸食水煙、容許他人在室內吸食水煙等罪。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177647/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"控煙酒辦檢走兩支水煙。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db307f83b1405b2b0e984b56ef38e51d/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_224519730_07_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        控煙酒辦檢走兩支水煙。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177648/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"控煙酒辦檢走兩支水煙。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/18cb571442ee799da63f1ab66f6defcb/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_224519730_06_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        控煙酒辦檢走兩支水煙。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177649/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e831262505148f70c1a1678409ede54a/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_224519730_02_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177650/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"控煙酒辦今晚到渣甸街66號一間樓上酒吧「放蛇」及執法。黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c50933ed397ca9921a7a8bd6100486f4/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_224519730_01_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        控煙酒辦今晚到渣甸街66號一間樓上酒吧「放蛇」及執法。黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4177651/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"黃文威攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/258b278d49d1edc20579210f72f78806/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250404_224519730_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃文威攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
